name: Roboto Inc "Selfie"
description:
Happy New Year! 5 years in this world of digital art and 7 months this year in HEN which have been incredible.
Thanks to the friends, the artists, the collectors who have shared with me all this time. I value and feel honored to contact you and your support that helps me to keep going forward giving the best of me and for the love of art.
Best wishes for Health, Prosperity and Abundance for 2022.
Let's continue to build together a decentralized NFT innovating an artistic vanguard and avoiding falling into comfort zones and advice of the old schemes that no longer serve today.
